race.comment: FIRE ME UP (1) is in hot form with back to back wins at this track, running a dazzling 25.16 two back following up with 25.05 last time. Can measure up on top win two back. ZIPPING LIPA (4) looks close to win after hitting the frame last run (25.50) at this track in a OPEN. Has first look at box 4 this time. Hard to beat again. EXTREME TENSION (2) has a strong record this trip with nine wins and eight placings from 24 starts. In the money last time at this track (25.43) in a Free For All, finishing a 5.5 lengths second. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. OXIDISATION (6) was below best last time at this track (26.12) in a OPEN, finishing a 14 length seventh. Has already won four times from this draw.
